{
  "stem": "2533.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I got known from the people I was after, they went to [NON-ENGLISH]-- they told me, stay where you are, because it's much better to be in a private house than in a factory with a lot of other people.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there, I had my own room, I had three meals a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They told me what to do, to clean and look after Peter, and to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hildemann taught me how--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hildemann.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me how to-- she told me, because every day there, there was almost the same thing during every week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like one day on a Tuesday, we had that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next Tuesday, we had the same thing, and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The place wasn't like it was at war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the bombs were coming so very often, and we had to run to shelters and all that, like bunkers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day I was on my bike to the eastern railway station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a very, very big bunker, and I got into the tram line, and I fell over, and people were running over me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I got back, I was bruised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know, I said to the Hildemanns, I'm not going anywhere, because he had a small bunker under the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, if I have to be killed, I'd rather be killed here, and not by people trampling all over me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't disagree.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I stayed there, because when they run to some places, I had time to take down the feather beds or the blankets or Peter's toys, or whatever he wanted and all that in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And most of all, I took down the radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know what I did?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
